## 3. Default Orchestration

The `harness` role is the default. When in doubt, read
`.agents/subagents/harness/SUBAGENT.md` and act as that role.

## 4. Hard Rules (Non-Negotiable)

- One feature in `in_progress` at a time.
- `./check.sh` must pass before declaring a feature `done`.
- For `sdd: true` features: spec → human approval → implement → review → done.
- Never edit the approved spec (`specs/<feature>/{requirements,design,tasks}.md` are read-only after approval).
- Every R<n> must end up with at least one test.

